title: Should we buy the Jenny 1 of 1 NFT from x0r for $8K?
body:
x0r made this piece, wants to sell it as a 1 of 1 to Jenny DAO: https://www.dropbox.com/s/kk04vdrw8zo7fqw/Jenny%20by%20x0r.GIF?dl=0

It'll be his second ever 1 of 1 (and first standalone 1 of 1), and it has the Jenny token's smart contract code in ASCII art in the form of an Inverted Jenny. 

Here is x0r's most recent Nifty drop for price reference: https://niftygateway.com/collections/x0r2
author: 0x3B4e9e284Bf2aD3F614949684439f70D6C1CE652
